Responsive Design: Enhance the front-end by ensuring it's fully responsive across various devices and screen sizes. Implement a mobile-first approach to make the platform accessible and user-friendly on smartphones, tablets, and desktops.

User-Friendly Dashboard: Create an intuitive and user-friendly dashboard with a clean and organized interface. Provide at-a-glance insights, data summaries, and clear navigation to streamline order management tasks for users.

Advanced Search and Filtering: Implement advanced search and filtering options that allow users to quickly find orders based on various criteria such as date, status, customer, or product. Provide real-time filtering and sorting for a seamless user experience.
